Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:28.25,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}…永遠普遍の愛なんて　信じられるのかしら？…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.42,0:22:35.10,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}甘い紅茶に溶かす　ため息模様
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.48,0:22:39.76,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もう　待ちくたびれたのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.86,0:22:48.09,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたを追いかけて　堕ちるワンダーランド
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.25,0:22:52.47,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どこまで行けばいいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:55.83,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}イロトリドリの闇を抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.13,0:23:02.33,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}道標の旋律　心が騒ぎだす
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.48,0:23:06.37,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}時計仕掛けの運命ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.46,0:23:10.06,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}壊してしまえ　私は自由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.27,0:23:13.44,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたが真実
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:21.25,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}Catcher in a Maze　生きる証
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:28.25,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}…是否能相信  所謂永恆的愛？…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.42,0:22:35.10,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}嘆息溶化於甘美紅茶  化為波紋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.48,0:22:39.76,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}已經  再也按捺不住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.86,0:22:48.09,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追尋著你  墜落往  Wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.25,0:22:52.47,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}何處才是盡頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:55.83,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}穿越色彩斑斕的黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.13,0:23:02.33,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}指明前路的旋律  踴動不已的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.48,0:23:06.37,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}假使命運如時鐘般不可逆轉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.46,0:23:10.06,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}破壞它  我將獲得自由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.27,0:23:13.44,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你是唯一的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:21.25,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}Catcher in a Maze  是我生存的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//ED
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.85,0:01:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲·貝薩流斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以定罪枷鎖之名
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.01,0:01:51.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此  對你做出裁決
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的罪名
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:02:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是你的存在本身
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體被拖拽著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被黑色的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:25.73,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路的孩子和黑色的兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…這裡到底是什麼鬼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管跑到哪  都是一樣的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…是在做惡夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說只要有人犯了重罪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯就會派使者前來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個  是來把這小鬼關進阿比斯的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:38.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  少爺  這位大人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.13,0:03:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  基爾  千萬別死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:03:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是看上去很好吃的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…  那到底是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是看上去很好吃的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是看上去很好吃的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是看上去很好吃的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是看上去很好吃的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是個撲克  居然這麼囂張
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是我先看上的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那個時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前就說過了  這傢伙可是我的私有物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許對他出手  死神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我性騷擾的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真弱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然被那種低級靈體玩弄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:16.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈體？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是誕生在阿比斯中的生命體的總稱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中撲克是很低等的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是靈體嗎  染血黑兔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:30.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈體都有襲擊人的習性嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次見到你的時候  你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會原諒你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對…  絕對不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想要殺我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？  你在胡說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次見到你的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.78,0:09:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從死神手中救了你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是記錯人了  真是個失禮的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  別把我和撲克那種東西混為一談…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～太好了～發現餅乾了耶～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子已經餓到快不行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是個奇怪的傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才還那麼慌張的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經不怕我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經習慣這個空間了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經看到許多不可思議的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以說是習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說早點接受現實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:10:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才能清楚地把握現狀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我被綁架的時候  奧斯卡叔叔說過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.57,0:10:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這種時候最要緊的是  保持冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綁架？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  你不是我的敵人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才又救了我一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神經大條嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  只不過是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  同意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把我當笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的真名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像黑兔子  染血黑兔這種名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是別人給我亂起的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我特別允許你叫我艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:54.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會有種很熟悉的感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是  不要誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.75,0:11:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我救你是有目的的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是為了你著想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得死神把你丟進這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便死掉的話  我可就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…你想要我做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想逃出阿比斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…一直在等像你這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠成為我的契約者的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契約者？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也覺察到了吧  這裡不是一般的監牢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯與你所在的世界是兩個不同次元的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同次元？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在兩個世界之間產生了被稱為通路的空間扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:12:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的力量在那裡強制打開出口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  我和你就都可以從這裡出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  現在的我力量受到限制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發揮不出足以打開出口的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.55,0:12:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠解除力量限制的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是契約
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要喊我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同意契約就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有必須去做的事  我要從這裡出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後你也想從這裡出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的目的相同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就讓我們聯手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  奧茲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏羅小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才真是好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.18,0:13:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才如果和她握手的話  會被殺掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您放心  奧茲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來接您的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏羅小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲大人被關進這裡以後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊因茲華斯家就立刻派人來救您了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到消息後  很擔心您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就一起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那前面  有可以傳送出去的魔法陣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:14:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請加油  很快就能到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在想那個靈體的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  沒有在想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙可是眾多靈體中  最危險的一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂契約  是指其存在本身不安定的靈體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了持續地存在於我們的世界  所必需的儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.73,0:14:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  那傢伙在成人儀式時現身了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只不過是靠這裡傳過去的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時現身而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候她那麼強…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前也發生過  每次通路被打開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她都會出現並干涉我們的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把自己選中的契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個個殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:15:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定是打算在最後殺掉奧茲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管那個了  我們快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的確是很不講道理  很可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她救了我兩次…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在說些什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關那傢伙的事  我完全不瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺她不像是個壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…我會有這種想法…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:39.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說些什麼呀  奧茲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是呢  我這人真是…啊哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲不僅對你表現出殺意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還對著你大喊要殺了你不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣還覺得她不是壞人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:15:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會知道艾莉絲的真名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.26,0:16:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我特別允許你叫我艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  艾莉絲要殺我這件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家還想再多玩一會兒的說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:38.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:46.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  愛給人添麻煩的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,染血黑兔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙叫瘋嬰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一種能窺視並玩弄人類記憶的靈體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牽我手的時候  猶豫了那麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.44,0:17:02.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對那女孩倒是很聽話  立馬就被牽走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:09.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡死掉的話  我可就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…為什麼你要做到這個地步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於你  我完全不瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要一定要選擇我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得對呢  我也是  對你一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就在我掙扎著想要出去時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了那個懷錶的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺到很熟悉的旋律  就追了過去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果就來到你身邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我就覺察到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那個  能夠帶我逃出阿比斯的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何根據
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不過是相信自己的直覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能解除限制的話  這種傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快逃吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這是在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:18:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想要救她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不知道她有什麼目的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道剛才的話是真是假
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我欠你的人情還沒還呢  怎麼能讓你死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我也不知道為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:30.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許我腦子不正常了  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.83,0:19:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想在這裡失去她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲  我要與你訂下契約
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯了喲  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是請您與我訂下契約  才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思維停止  身體在拒絕在反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.18,0:20:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法抵抗的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在體內蹂躪著…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:32.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該為能夠成為我的東西而感到榮幸  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於…終於到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下力量的限制解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能逃離阿比斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.48,0:21:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷克？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真是…太令人驚喜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他靠自己的力量從阿比斯逃出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.63,0:21:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情…怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.18,0:21:44.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從結果來看這樣不是很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.67,0:21:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於得到薩布耶里特的悲劇之鑰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.81,0:22:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  已經沒有退路了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這位大人  是會帶來毀滅的墮天使
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.88,0:23:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}那隻黑兔子現在在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.80,0:23:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}通路……要連接上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.88,0:23:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}現在你也是一個名符其實的「違法契約者」了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.10,0:23:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}我沒有記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.26,0:23:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}還記得的  就只有艾莉絲這個名字……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.60,0:24:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}不要再傷害艾莉絲了！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.11,0:24:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}這是在試探我嗎……很好！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.73,0:24:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  晨暉映照之地